            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-navy">Can this improve with home strategies?</h4>
              <p class="text-sm">Absolutely. Modifying the environment and reducing morning demands is highly effective for children with ADHD.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-navy">Do I need an assessment?</h4>
